body:
So... in my own headcanon, she pops out men from some teleportional device through nonsensical anime bullcrap with some super high-tech...thingy attached to them and she's the only one who can bring the bad guys more men from other dimensions, but they can only do it through insane amounts of sex.

It's stupid as f*ck, but it's still less gross than the idea of her birthing fully grown men just shortly after getting knocked up.
